## Modifications

This repository ("Whisper_plus") is a modified version of the Whisper model originally developed by OpenAI.
The modifications include changes to the timestamp generation logic to produce shorter segments and more frequent timestamps.

### Summary of Modifications:

- Modified LICENSE file
- Added option to change segment length in `DecodingOptions` class
- Changes, to README.md, requirements.txt, .gitignore, etc.
- Changes in view of the PyPI package name

### Ownership of Modifications

The modifications made in this fork are provided under the same MIT License terms.
While the original Whisper model is owned by OpenAI, the modifications and the new version of this repository are managed by AppSolves. 

